{"tid":2506471,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"韓粉10餘人大亂鬥有人被打到腦震盪 里長、杏仁哥起訴","createTime":"2021-04-27T10:37:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T10:47:46.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"487ff6af134af724aae592a89a223e7f1cbe844b","tid":2506471,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:37:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qlVyav2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqlVyav2.gif&h=3ca14ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓粉指標人物「最強菜農」林佳新與內門「石頭里長」謝振城等人，去年11月30日，因於<br />\n網路直播過程中雙方「理念不合」發生口角，進而「落人」相約在高雄市內門區中埔里里<br />\n長服務處理論，林等人開車自雲林南下，被10餘人包夾在服務處外，謝當場嗆「打死他們<br />\n我負責」，混亂中林陣營多部轎車被砸，4人受傷，有人被打到腦震盪，橋頭地檢署今天<br />\n依妨害秩序罪起訴謝以及參與其中的「杏仁哥」等人。<br />\n <br />\n檢方調查，謝振城去年11月30日21時許於網路直播過程中，提到與林佳新理念不合，林隨<br />\n後撥打電話予謝欲澄清，雙方於電話中因細故發生口角爭執，林隨即找了5人駕2部車自雲<br />\n林縣南下高雄市，與謝相約在內門中埔里里長服務處碰頭。<br />\n <br />\n謝知悉林要南下找他理論，也邀約「杏仁哥」一同商討教訓林佳新，並透過不明人士，找<br />\n了10餘人攜帶棍棒、木劍、木椅、木刀、鋤頭木柄等凶器前往。<br />\n <br />\n林佳新等人深夜被包夾在服務外，進退不得，謝從服務處走出來，一聲令下「打死他們我<br />\n負責」，一旁的杏仁哥也幫腔「一個都不要讓他們跑掉」，一夥人開始對林座車猛砸，造<br />\n成車窗、板金、保險桿損毀，另一輛轎車見前車被砸，嚇得倒車欲駛離，仍被攔下，車上<br />\n4人被拉出來毆打，打到四肢多處挫擦傷、骨折、以及腦震盪，警方獲報趕往現場才平息<br />\n。<br />\n <br />\n橋頭地檢署今天依妨害秩序等罪起訴包括謝振城、杏仁哥及另5名參與鬥毆的男子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3512948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3512948&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oO2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=ed7ed58d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fsociety%2Fbreakingnews%2F3512948&h=5a17547b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/society/breakingnews/3512948</a>"},{"pid":"c5b97ac4e2bb8454a07df8cec1c85070b8f5f8de","tid":2506471,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:43:02.000Z","msg":"On99 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe9de9adfb9c13dcc4577ef95efdd6a8c34b3fd","tid":2506471,"uid":4767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:45:02.000Z","msg":"打贏先係真韓粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65a0787cc0f52107ad0731bf3d8837a71b18be4","tid":2506471,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:45:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVrdaU9MLkVW1oDqhjgp2Rz1AUKvs86fpDebjkiZLpG2i?filename=mNxYaKL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmNxYaKL.jpg&h=1497e72c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZCxr2bd1sihwPYsMdoGrcRFqCe4Fzz638SMu1eHAkHUm?filename=FgBaMh5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFgBaMh5.jpg&h=939546bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"67a97f089bbc732f773457157a38432196b66f9b","tid":2506471,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"打贏咁點丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}